OL,3,C'Doors need to be opened for working
OL,4,Cclass people to get into acting'
OL,6,FAward winning Welsh actor Rakie Ayola
OL,7,Fsays "lots of doors need to be opened"
OL,8,Ffor people from working class
OL,9,Fbackgrounds to get into the performing
OL,10,Farts industry.
OL,12,FIn a candid interview with Nest
OL,13,FJenkins on ITV Wales' , 'The Pact'
OL,14,Factor said a lot has changed since she
OL,15,Ffirst started acting.
OL,17,FWhen asked if enough is being done to
OL,18,Fencourage people from working class
OL,19,Fbackgrounds, she said "lots of doors
OL,20,Fneed to be opened."
