OL,3,C'Doors need to be opened for working
OL,4,Cclass people to get into acting'
OL,6,FShe added: "We're making it really
OL,7,Fdifficult for people who don't have
OL,8,Fmoney. I know that I went to Welsh
OL,9,FCollege of Music and Drama before it
OL,10,Fwas Royal and I went there on a full
OL,11,Fgrant from the education authority
OL,12,Fthat paid my rent and my fee.
OL,14,F"I did National New Theatre of Wales
OL,15,Fwith Michael Sheen and Ruth Jones and
OL,16,Fmy four weeks residential course was
OL,17,Fpaid for because my dad didn't have
OL,18,Fany money.
OL,20,F"I don't think those streams of grants
OL,21,Fnow exist coming to performing arts."
