OL,6,FA star of both stage and screen, multi-
OL,7,Faward winning actor Rakie Ayola had
OL,8,Fher big break on the hit ITV show
OL,9,FSoldier Soldier in 1993.
OL,11,FBorn in the Ely area of Cardiff, her
OL,12,Fcareer spans over three decades.
OL,14,FShe has featured in Black Mirror,
OL,15,FDoctor Who and played the role of
OL,16,FHermione in the Harry Potter stage
OL,17,Fplay.
OL,19,FMore recently, she has been working
OL,20,Fbehind the scenes as a producer for
OL,21,Fthe short film, Hedgehog.
