OL,3,C'Doors need to be opened for working
OL,4,Cclass people to get into acting'
OL,6,FAyola said it is important to
OL,7,Fcelebrate other women in the industry.
OL,8,FShe said "if one person moves forward,
OL,9,Fthen we all move forward.
OL,11,F"Most of the women that are in my
OL,12,Ftypical casting bracket, are in my
OL,13,Fphonebook. They are my friends. I
OL,14,Fcelebrate their successes and they
OL,15,Fcelebrate mine."
OL,17,FIn 2023, Rakie Ayola was the 18th
OL,18,Frecipient of the prestigious BAFTA
OL,19,FCymru Sian Phillips Award.
