OL,3,C'Doors need to be opened for working
OL,4,Cclass people to get into acting'
OL,6,FAyola said it is important to amplify
OL,7,Fvoices from marginalised communities.
OL,9,FShe said: "There are a lot of stories
OL,10,Fto tell. Of course, we shouldn't stop
OL,11,Ftelling the stories that we've
OL,12,Ftraditionally told.
OL,14,F"But let's open the doors to telling
OL,15,Fnew stories and telling old stories in
OL,16,Fdifferent ways. It's about just
OL,17,Fkeeping theatre alive really and
OL,18,Fkeeping it relevant.
