OL,3,C'Doors need to be opened for working
OL,4,Cclass people to get into acting'
OL,6,F"And don't be afraid of a history that
OL,7,Fyou didn't know and a history that
OL,8,Fmight not be positive.
OL,10,F"Let's investigate it and let's look
OL,11,Fat it from different angles. Let's
OL,12,Funderstand how we got to where we are
OL,13,Fand try to do it better moving
OL,14,Fforward."
OL,16,FAyola said the industry is "getting
OL,17,Fbetter" but things "need to keep
OL,18,Fchanging".
