OL,3,C'Doors need to be opened for working
OL,4,Cclass people to get into acting'
OL,6,FShe said: "It's absolutely getting
OL,7,Fbetter. The fact that I'm still doing
OL,8,Fit, the fact that I'm sat here and I'm
OL,9,Fstill doing new things.
OL,11,F"After all these decades and I'm still
OL,12,Fable to do new things. So, yes there's
OL,13,Fchange but we need to keep changing.
OL,14,FBut don't be afraid to share and let's
OL,15,Fmake the table bigger and let's add
OL,16,Fmore chairs to the table.
OL,18,F"I'm here because Cardiff has a very
OL,19,Frich West African tradition. Let's not
OL,20,Fbe afraid of that and let's celebrate
OL,21,Fit."
